<p>
<note n="0154001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0154001">Mahāsammatarāja 譯為世界最初之王，卡許摩訶，卡所許，大平等、大同意、民主、大王等。</note>
<note n="0154002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0154002">卡魯利耶尼與瓦羅卡魯利耶尼。</note>
<note n="0154003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0154003">協會本，為卡魯耶那迦。</note>
<note n="0155004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155004">梵語 Ikṣvāku 懿摩〔師〕，伊摩，甘庶、為釋迦族之祖次摩訶三摩多為重要之王。</note>
<note n="0155005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155005">釋尊之祖父。星賀賀努。</note>
<note n="0155006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155006">釋迦族之分族拘利族之都城。</note>
<note n="0155007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155007">協會本，為安迦那。</note>
<note n="0156008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0156008">師子頰有四王八子，他書不出此名。</note>
</p>
